  "title": "Lab Technician ( East, Office hours ) #HCT",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Sample Receipt & Handling: Receive daily shipments of samples, assess them upon arrival, and store them according to specific protocols.</li></ul><ul><li>Data Entry: Enter sample information into the ICON lab database with high accuracy.</li></ul><ul><li>Documentation & Quality Check: Perform quality checks on paperwork, scan documents, and manage inventory logs.</li></ul><ul><li>Lab Support: Barcode label, validate specimens, and transfer samples to technicians for analysis.</li></ul><ul><li>Compliance: Adhere to safety regulations (OSHA) and internal company procedures at all times.</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Education: High School Diploma or a Diploma/Degree in a Life Sciences or related field.</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates please send a copy of your resume in MS Word to</p><p><u><strong>Clinicalresearch@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p></p><p>Cameron Tan</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W</p><p>EA Licence No. 99C4599</p>",
